# Adding Reproducibility Checks

## Check ID Prefixes
- `DEP-` dependency management
- `PATH-` filesystem path issues
- `DOC-` documentation
- `ENV-` environment / containerization
- `ML-` machine learning specific
- `BIO-` bioinformatics / genomics
- `CLI-` climate model specific
- `STAT-` statistics / data analysis
- `MEM-` org memory pattern match

## Required Pattern
```python
findings.append(Finding(
    check_id="XX-NNN",
    title="Short descriptive title",
    severity=Severity.CRITICAL,  # or HIGH, MEDIUM, LOW, INFO
    description="Why this matters for reproducibility.",
    file_path=path_if_applicable,
    line_number=line_if_applicable,
    suggestion="Concrete fix instruction.",
))
```

## After Adding a Check
1. Add field multiplier in `scoring/engine.py` if domain-critical
2. Add inverse bonus in `_compute_bonuses()` if good practice
3. Update check ID table in `.claude/SKILL.md`
